{"type":null,"faqId":31900,"title":"系统运行缓慢，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以尝试以下方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>当前运行的应用程序过多，请关闭一些暂时不用的应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 应用管理 &gt; 正在运行”，点击当前不需要使用的应用程序，然后点击“停止”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=99044\" style=\"width:5.164583in;height:2.4659722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <span>安装的应用程序太多，系统盘空间不足，导致系统运行缓慢。可以卸载一些应用程序，释放系统盘空间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕长按需要卸载的应用程序，并将其拖动至“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=99045\" style=\"width:0.33055556in;height:0.24444444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=99046\" style=\"width:2.4666667in;height:3.7541666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span>重启手机，系统会自动关闭暂时不用的进程及应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=99047\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6420","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287942000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":187,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":1,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"系统运行,系统慢,卡,卡顿,不流畅","avgScore":1.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}